          <div class="flex justify-between border-t border-neutral-800 pt-3"><span class="text-neutral-500">Peso</span><span class="text-neutral-300">280g (universal)</span></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-t border-neutral-800 pt-3"><span class="text-neutral-500">Ventilação</span><span class="text-neutral-300">22 aberturas</span></div>
