          <div class="flex justify-between border-t border-neutral-800 pt-3"><span class="text-neutral-500">Ajuste</span><span class="text-neutral-300">Roc Loc Sport MIPS</span></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-t border-neutral-800 pt-3"><span class="text-neutral-500">Tamanhos</span><span class="text-neutral-300">Universal (54–61cm)</span></div>
